    v1 = wp.cos((tmp + 0.95))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.29)
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.21) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.07)))
    v1 = 0.96
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.99) * 0.14) + ((tmp + 0.21 - v0 + 0.49) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.02)))
